1 0 0 1 56 732.0 Tm (From Semaphore to Signal: The Contested Invention of the Three-Colour Traffic Light, 1868-1935) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 56 718.0 Tm () Tj
/F1 9 Tf
1 0 0 1 56 704.0 Tm (Rowena Castellanos) Tj
